data.text:
SEO potential

Casema.nl has a Google Pagerank of 7 out of 10 and an Alexa Rank of 700,412. Although being more and more depreciated as a website quality indicator, a higher PageRank still indicates in most cases the popularity of a website. Sites with high Alexa Rank have high amounts of visitors, indicating that they get good search engine rankings.

The domain name was created 2026 years ago (year: 0000, month: 00, day: 00) and has a length of 6 characters. Search engines algorithm gives more credibility and authority to websites whose domain name has been registered for a long time and is still in use (but not parked).

It is given a rating of C, due to its good performance.
